Class AbstractReversibleList<E>

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EvictingList

    public abstract class AbstractReversibleList<E>
extends com.google.common.collect.ForwardingList<E>
implements List<E>
    An abstract List implementation which provides methods for accessing elements from the end of the list. Extending classes must implement ForwardingList.delegate(); see ForwardingList for more details. This class is not thread-safe.
    Author:
    nwinant
